########################################
### 📋 REGISTROS
########################################

### LISTAR
GET http://localhost:3000/registros

###

### CRIAR
POST http://localhost:3000/registros
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_ambiente": 1,
  "id_instrutor": 1,
  "id_turma": 1,
  "data_inicio": "2026-04-16 14:00:00",
  "data_fim": "2026-04-16 16:00:00"
}

###

### BUSCAR POR ID
GET http://localhost:3000/registros/1

###

### ATUALIZAR
PUT http://localhost:3000/registros/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_ambiente": 1,
  "id_instrutor": 1,
  "id_turma": 1,
  "data_inicio": "2026-04-16 15:00:00",
  "data_fim": "2026-04-16 17:00:00"
