########################################
### 📊 RELATÓRIOS
########################################

### GERAR RELATÓRIO
POST http://localhost:3000/relatorios/gerar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data_inicio": "2026-01-01 00:00:00",
  "data_fim": "2026-12-31 23:59:59",
  "ambiente": "",
  "instrutor": "",
  "turma": ""
}

###

### DOWNLOAD (trocar nome depois de gerar)
GET http://localhost:3000/relatorios/download/relatorio_EXEMPLO.txt

###

### DELETAR RELATÓRIO
DELETE http://localhost:3000/relatorios/delete/relatorio_EXEMPLO.txt